metadata.name: 2002-TII
metadata.description:
NO AIRBAGS

Inspired by the dangerous love between car and human. This love is based on having the power to destroy each other and not using this power.

No Airbags brings history's most iconic car designs to the blockchain. Each piece comes with a unique sound design that refers to its era. No Airbags collectors also physically add handmade toys to their collections.
